CREST Singapore was launched in July 2016 as a partnership with the Association of Information Security Professionals (AISP), 
with the support of the Cyber Security Agency of Singapore (CSA). 
This initiative was developed in collaboration with the Monetary Authority of Singapore (MAS), 
the Association of Banks in Singapore (ABS) and the Infocom Development Authority of Singapore (IDA).

CREST (Singapore) Working Committee
In partnership with Cyber Security Agency of Singapore (CSA) and the Association of Information Security Professionals, 
the CREST Singapore Chapter was the first CREST Chapter established in Asia.  
The CREST Singapore Working Committee has been set up to oversee the Chapterâ€™s efforts in Cyber Security professional development 
and CREST-related activities. 
